commit.message: Can now handle multiple game pitch files
Link to pitch zone image map
Readme update to add pitch zone

Require file extension when using `svg()` helper

This matches how the `inline_svg` gem works for Rails:
https://github.com/jamesmartin/inline_svg

Having it mimic Inline SVG makes it easier on developers to move between
Middleman and Rails.

Improve error-handling of SVG helper

Co-authored-by: Tyson Gach <tyson@tysongach.com>
Co-authored-by: Full Name <ward@thoughtbot.com>

Rename `.sample.env` to `.env.sample`

This sorts the two files next to each other.

Add a `.tool-versions` file for asdf

We've changed our recommended tool manager to asdf, which uses the
`.tool-versions` file to manage, well, tool versions.
